data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite residence offering three bedrooms and over 1,500 square feet of living space. Experience the pinnacle of safety and style with impact glass sliders and windows throughout. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a built-in pantry, and wood cabinets with soft-close hinges. Indulge in the luxury of the generous master suite, boasting two walk-in closets and a beautifully appointed master bath complete with double sinks. This remarkable property sits on over a 1-acre lot, providing ample space for your aspirations. The home includes a 2-car garage for your convenience. Step into the outdoor haven, where a covered patio beckons for moments of relaxation. Inside, revel in the contemporary appeal of wood-look tile, while the bathrooms are adorned with elegant granite countertops. A dedicated laundry room adds practicality to your daily routine.
This property is not just a home; it's a testament to comfort, elegance, and thoughtful design. Welcome to a lifestyle defined by quality and sophistication.
